
  **** WebServerBenchmark README ****


  Welcome

     SERVER

        apache , lighttd ,

        nodejs , warp+yesod ,

        tomcat , jetty


     BENCHMARK CLIENT TOOL

        ab apache benchmark tool


  DIR

    WebServerBenchmark/
       server/              each server's configuration and some source.
          apache/
          lighttpd/
          nodejs/
          warp/
          j2ee/

       client/              benchmarking shell
          result/
          images/


  APACHE

    setup:

        server config => conf/http-*.conf or conf/extra/http-mpm.conf


    command:

                  == start ==
        $ cd apache
        $ ./run.sh prefork|worker|event start

                  == stop ==
        $ cd apache
        $ ./run.sh prefork|worker|event stop


